    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/cae0aaee414b23385001346e0559831b.avif?t=1770679931\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/0d1565ea515403e66c65b4a289165aa0.avif?t=1770679931\" width=1560 height=468 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ETRE is a 3D third-person Metroidvania set inside Orbis, a planet-scale alien mind on the brink of awakening. Explore a vast, interconnected labyrinth of luminous architecture, solve spatial puzzles, and engage in fluid ground and aerial combat as you search for your lost love and decide what this new intelligence will become. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Xyle, drawn across the stars by a signal from Orbis. Atel, your bonded other, has vanished inside, and a post-human society called the Etre has grown within the World Mind’s body, split between two factions who each want to use Orbis for their own ends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Across distinct biomes inspired by the visionary sci‑fi of 70s–80s European graphic novels, you’ll uncover a network of living machines called Angel Tech and the rogue Living Geometry spawned by their corruption. Over a journey with multiple endings, your choices and discoveries shape whether Orbis stabilizes as a new world, becomes a transcendent god-mind, or awakens into something far more terrifying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/8fe9abac5ec1c1e02137e9cfbdec0975.poster.avif?t=1770679931\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/8fe9abac5ec1c1e02137e9cfbdec0975.webm?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/8fe9abac5ec1c1e02137e9cfbdec0975.mp4?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/d2ff872cd3773a7839d72b3cc4da4f48.avif?t=1770679931\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast, interconnected 3D labyrinth inside an alien mind, with abilities that open new paths through familiar spaces. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Lucent Drift to gain verticality, manipulate machines, and scan the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/24f99e900b84779d9d1894b1c4da9575.poster.avif?t=1770679931\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/24f99e900b84779d9d1894b1c4da9575.webm?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/24f99e900b84779d9d1894b1c4da9575.mp4?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/554a89ec419b7f50aef536956159ee7a.poster.avif?t=1770679931\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/554a89ec419b7f50aef536956159ee7a.webm?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/554a89ec419b7f50aef536956159ee7a.mp4?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/0a505656dafddfd7d4b721eff436bc0d.avif?t=1770679931\" width=780 height=68 /></span>Switch between grounded and aerial combat, destroying, subduing, or repurposing strange machines and anomalies as tools and allies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront the Living Geometry in boss encounters that play like duels and riddles, demanding both reflexes and understanding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/057c7a80e8579227102b2f6b0c0cf128.poster.avif?t=1770679931\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/057c7a80e8579227102b2f6b0c0cf128.webm?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/057c7a80e8579227102b2f6b0c0cf128.mp4?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/8477659904119d0a200837d7e25aa8a9.avif?t=1770679931\" width=780 height=68 /></span>Follow in the footsteps of Atel, your bonded one and navigate the competing visions of Mal and Weyl, two Etre leaders with incompatible plans for Orbis and Lucent, the structured light that forms this world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece together a non-linear story about love, awakening, and responsibility as you follow Atel’s echoes and map your entanglement with the World Mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/0e0516cef1a53d9767680f5bfde8bad9.poster.avif?t=1770679931\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/0e0516cef1a53d9767680f5bfde8bad9.webm?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/0e0516cef1a53d9767680f5bfde8bad9.mp4?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/88c68f87fef080a4520eb1495c7eb3c4.poster.avif?t=1770679931\" width=800 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/88c68f87fef080a4520eb1495c7eb3c4.webm?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391940/extras/88c68f87fef080a4520eb1495c7eb3c4.mp4?t=1770679931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p>",
